# LLM Rules

- ALL prompt strings live in `llm/prompt_builder.py` ONLY — the single source of truth
- If self-improvement modifies a prompt, archive old version in `prompts/archive/`
- Model routing via `llm/router.py` — score complexity → pick tier (nano/fast/smart/vision)
- Latency budgets: nano < 100ms, fast < 1s, smart < 15s first token
- ReAct++ loop: THOUGHT → PLAN → ACTION → OBSERVATION → CRITIQUE → REVISE → RESPOND
- CriticAgent scores: accuracy, completeness, safety, helpfulness
- Streaming via `llm/streaming.py` — sentence-level chunks for TTS
- TabbyAPI (ExLlamaV2) is primary backend; Ollama for vision + embedding
